high_descs: Turn to the left to move to the sink.
Pick up the potato from the sink, on the left side.
Carry the potato and turn to the left, then face the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and place the potato inside. Shut the door then open it again. Remove the potato and shut the door.
Carry the potato and take a step to the left.
Place the potato in the trash can, to the left of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato and throw it away.

high_descs: Pick up potato from sink, to left of egg.
Turn left, proceed to refrigerator.  Turn right to face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, place potato between tomato and mug, close refrigerator.  Wait four seconds, open door to refrigerator, remove potato, close door.
Turn left to go to end of refrigerator.  Turn right to face refrigerator.  Look down.
Place potato in garbage can to the left of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Move potato from sink, put in refrigerator.  Remove from refrigerator, put in garbage.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the potato in the left basin, to the left of the egg.
Turn right and walk to the fridge at the end of the counter.
Place the potato in the fridge to the right of the mug. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Put the potato in the black bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato in a garbage bin.
